room_title: Escape room "The Iron Throne" by Fort Wayne Escape Room in Fort Wayne
room_address: 327 E Wayne St #200 Fort Wayne, IN 46802
room_description:
The Army of the Dead is marching towards Westeros! You have seen the Night Kings Forces, yet have been unable to convince any of the Great Houses. After pleading with Cersei Lannister, she claims all members of your group have gone mad. You are now being held prisoner somewhere inside a sprawling Westeros Castle.
With only days until the White Walkers reach the Wall, you must not only find a way to escape alive but also find a way to prove that the great war is here!
